TextBody:
Hello Stephen,

In order to check if the hotfix was applied, you can check in Dashboard -> Live Update -> View Applied EPP Software Updates. If the hotfix shows up in this list, then the patch was applied successfully.

The hotfix will not disappear from the available updates list even if it is applied.
After the EPP Server will be updated to the 5940 version the hotfix will disappear from the available updates list.

Best regards,
Emil
